### ==========================================
### CATEGORY ENDPOINTS
### ==========================================

### Crear Categoría 1
POST http://localhost:8080/api/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Electrónica"
}

### Crear Categoría 2
POST http://localhost:8080/api/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Hogar"
}

### Listar todas las categorías
GET http://localhost:8080/api/categories

### Obtener categoría ID 1
GET http://localhost:8080/api/categories/1

### Actualizar categoría ID 1
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/categories/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Electrónica y Computación"
}

### Desactivar categoría ID 2 (debe devolver 204)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/categories/2

### Desactivar categoría ya desactivada (debe fallar 409)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/categories/2

### ==========================================
### PRODUCT ENDPOINTS
### ==========================================

### Crear Producto OK (requiere categoryId activo)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "categoryId": 1,
  "name": "Teclado Mecánico",
  "sku": "TEC-MEC-001",
  "costPrice": 50.00,
  "salePrice": 120.00,
  "currentStock": 10
}

### Crear Producto 2
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "categoryId": 1,
  "name": "Mouse Gamer",
  "sku": "MOUSE-GAMER-001",
  "costPrice": 20.00,
  "salePrice": 60.00,
  "currentStock": 50
}

### Listar todos los productos
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products

### Obtener producto ID 1
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/1

### Actualizar producto ID 1
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/products/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Teclado Mecánico RGB",
  "sku": "TEC-RGB-001",
  "costPrice": 55.00,
  "salePrice": 150.00,
  "currentStock": 20
}

### Desactivar producto ID 1
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/products/1

### Desactivar producto ya desactivado (debe fallar 409)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/products/1

### ==========================================
### STOCK MOVEMENT ENDPOINTS
### ==========================================

### Registrar ingreso de stock (IN)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/stock-movements
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": 1,
  "quantity": 20,
  "type": "IN",
  "reason": "Compra a proveedor"
}

### Registrar egreso de stock (OUT)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/stock-movements
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": 1,
  "quantity": 5,
  "type": "OUT",
  "reason": "Venta mostrador"
}

### Registrar ajuste de stock (ADJUSTMENT positivo)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/stock-movements
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": 1,
  "quantity": 2,
  "type": "ADJUSTMENT",
  "reason": "Ajuste por inventario físico"
}

### Listar movimientos por producto (paginado)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/stock-movements?productId=1&page=0&size=10

### Listar página 2
GET http://localhost:8080/api/stock-movements?productId=1&page=1&size=2

### Registrar OUT sin stock suficiente (debe fallar 409)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/stock-movements
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": 1,
  "quantity": 9999,
  "type": "OUT",
  "reason": "Esto debería fallar"
}
